      <scopecontent id="aspace_89407f58f518640868eecd7c0534e58c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of 16mm films and a videotape produced by the Yale Office of Development. Included are "Tradition of Leadership," "Yale: 275th Year," and "Why Yale Needs All that Money."</p>  
      </scopecontent>
